
# TO RUN TEST CASES WITH COVERAGE
All files should end with spec.js`
Run this command from root of project.

istanbul cover _mocha -- test/backend-tests -R spec

To send coverage data to CodeClimate
Run this command from coverage folder
CODECLIMATE_REPO_TOKEN=e89e6b538c9f89968698ec93394f04bf04fb008d052473b05ad5d2264427a0b0 codeclimate < lcov.info
